title: Car Mechanic Simulator 2018 Plymouth Update v1 5 4-PLAZA

Car Mechanic Simulator 2018 - Plymouth Update v1.5.4 (c) PlayWay S.A

Release Date: 12/2017 Protection: Steam

3. Install update
4. Copy crack from the PLAZA folder
5. Play!

Block the game's exe in your firewall to prevent the game from
trying to go online

to run this game with admin privileges instead
